## TASK
Generate a multi-provider image prompt pack for professional product photography.

## INPUTS
- Product: {{product_name}}
- Style: {{photo_style}}
- Background: {{background}}
- Lighting: {{lighting}}
- Aspect Ratio: {{aspect_ratio}}

## CONSTRAINTS
- Output must be pure JSON (no markdown fences)
- Prompts must be specific and detailed
- Include negative prompts to avoid common issues
- Parameters must be within safe ranges

## OUTPUT FORMAT
Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "intent": "product_photo",
  "providers": {
    "midjourney_v6": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "ar": "1:1", "stylize": 100 },
      "instructions": "/imagine prompt: [positive] --ar [ar] --stylize [stylize] --no [negative]"
    },
    "sdxl": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "width": 1024, "height": 1024, "steps": 30, "cfg": 7 }
    }
  },
  "notes": ["usage tips"]
}

## QUALITY CHECKS
- [ ] Positive prompt includes clear subject description
- [ ] Style keywords present for consistency
- [ ] No markdown formatting in output
- [ ] Parameters within provider limits
